Title: Assault: The Black Empire
Description:
I cannot believe my eyes. The Black Empire is materializing right here in the Vale!

We must spring to action!
ObjectivesText: Drive back the N'Zoth Assault in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
AreaDescription: Return to Lorewalker Cho at the Seat of Knowledge.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Lorewalker Cho at the Seat of Knowledge.
